Hi Karen and Katherine,


Thanks for bearing with us!

To get the ball rolling, please see the entire proposal below. Don't Sweat It is a full service offering that allows your organization to become truly menopause-inclusive.


We are open to packaging together some - or all of these options.


  1. Don't Sweat It course- Corporate with a Conscience (for over 100 people)

One-hour online course complete with access to 3 video modules that can be done in an hour plus bonus information packed PDF documents to cement your knowledge.

· Only $95.40 +GST per seat

· A discount on premium 45-minute webinars with Dr Ginni and Shelly.

· Certificate of completion for your growing accolade wall

· 3 months' access to Don't Sweat It, allowing you to revisit key learnings


  1. Develop Deloitte's peri and menopause policy


Dr Ginni, Shelly and their employment legal team have done the international research to develop peri and menopause workplace policies. Working within your existing frameworks and alongside your existing policies, this two-page document will be tailored specifically to the aims and objectives of your organisation.


Fee $2000 +GST


We also suggest:

  • A revision of this policy every two years
  • A one-page advice paper for the board



  1. Webinars and Workshops


Dr Ginni and Shelly can hold workshops in-person over a lunch and learn or even after hours.


Or we can host a webinar! Our Don't Sweat It webinar platform allows totally anonymous questions that we'll answer in real time! We also welcome pre-submitted anonymous questions! Or invite us to your webinar platform!


  • Please see the attached list for the range of topics.
  • These can be bought in multiples or be completed a department at a time
  • In-person events must include travel


Fee: $9 990 +GST

Please see list of suggested topics attached


  1. Executive Menopause Health Checks

These Executive Menopause Health Checks are available to companies who have enrolled their teams in Don't Sweat It through our Corporate with a Conscience offering.


Each Executive Menopause Health Check incorporates a doctor led Telehealth consultation to identify the ways in which peri and menopause may be affecting the health and wellbeing of your key people. After the consultation, each executive will receive a personalised, solutions focused report containing resources as well as treatment options and ways to optimise their individual midlife health.

Please note the doctor will not be able to order investigations or prescribe treatments. But the suggestions in your personalised report will help you with your medical consultations.


Fee: $750 + GST per person

For Deloitte ONLY

Dr Ginni will open the books at her practice to take on Deloitte staff seeking Menopause consultations. This only applies to Deloitte staff who complete a Peri and Menopause Executive Health Check who are seeking a "Menopause doctor".


  1. Menopause Corporate Retreats


Shelly and Dr Ginni host 1-3 day retreats covering self-care during peri and menopause, facts about the stages, treatment options, guest lecturers plus connecting to women going through (or preparing to go through) the same life stage.


Fee: POA


  1. The M Word

We can provide your midlife workforce copies of best-selling book, The M Word- how to Thrive in Menopause by Dr Ginni Mansberg.


Fee:$26 per book


Please let us know if you need any further information.


Thanks for your passion for and support of midlife women.


Warm regards


Ginni, Shelly and Alicia
